            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ὁ δῆμος ὁ Ἀθηναίων καὶ <supplied reason="lost">οἱ</supplied> τὴν ν<supplied reason="lost">ῆσον</supplied> <lb n="2"/>οἰκοῦντες βα<supplied reason="lost">σιλέα Ἀρχ</supplied>έλαον φιλό<lb break="no" n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">π</supplied>α&amp;lt;τ&amp;gt;ριν καὶ φιλοκ<supplied reason="lost">αίσαρα ἀρ</supplied>ετῆς ἕνεκ<supplied reason="lost">εν</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">καὶ</supplied> εὐσ<supplied reason="lost">εβείας τῆς εἰς τὸ ἱερόν</supplied>, <lb n="5"/>Ἀπό<supplied reason="lost">λλωνι</supplied>.
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Abweichende Textgestaltung.</p>
